org.hps.analysis.trigger

Enum TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver.TriggerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver.TriggerType>
      • org.hps.analysis.trigger.TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver.TriggerType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver.TriggerType>
    Enclosing class:
    TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver

    private static enum TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver.TriggerType
extends Enum<TriggerDiagnostic2019Driver.TriggerType>
    Enumerable TriggerType represents the supported types of trigger for the HPS experiment. It also provides a means to determine the trigger number as an int, where applicable, and a human-readable trigger name.

    TriggerType.ordinal() is also used as an index for multiple value-tracking arrays throughout the class.
